  "page": "Lyanna (disambiguation)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/index.php/Lyanna_Stark\" title=\"Lyanna Stark\">Lyanna Stark</a></b> was the sister of Lord Eddard Stark.\n</p><p>Other characters named <b>Lyanna</b> include:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Lyanna_Mormont\" title=\"Lyanna Mormont\">Lyanna Mormont</a>, the youngest daughter of Lady Maege Mormont</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lyanna_Stark_(daughter_of_Cregan)\" title=\"Lyanna Stark (daughter of Cregan)\">Lyanna Stark (daughter of Cregan)</a>, the youngest daughter of Lord Cregan Stark</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lyanna_(disambiguation)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: See also\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Elyana_Vypren\" title=\"Elyana Vypren\">Elyana Vypren</a>, the daughter of Lord Lucias Vypren</li>\n<li><i><a href=\"/index.php/Lady_Lyanna\" title=\"Lady Lyanna\">Lady Lyanna</a></i>, a war galley of the royal fleet</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Layna\" title=\"Layna\">Layna</a>, the daughter of an owner of an alehouse on the Goldroad</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lyanne_Glover\" title=\"Lyanne Glover\">Lyanne Glover</a>, the first wife of Lord Willam Stark</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Lyarra_Stark\" title=\"Lyarra Stark\">Lyarra Stark</a>, the youngest daughter of Rodrik Stark</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403120953\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.003 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.004 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 3/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function